=======

A short break from the regular ups..
Not for the squeamish, not for squares.

Extreme lives, modern primitives, life as art?
Give it a name.

Nineties documentary focusing on extreme sports and extreme body modifications.
Features Jim Rose as narrator and interviews with Cliff Cadaver, Steve Haworth and John Fitterer.

Along side such modifications and rites as transdermal mohawks , nasallangs and suicide suspension, is footage of skateboarders, surfers, snowboarders and B.A.S.E. jumping.

Don't miss Seth's where-the-f*ck-was-he-going air.
